'''印度国家证券交易所''' ('''NSE''')是一个位于印度[[孟买|孟买]]的[[证券交易所|证券交易所]]，是[[印度|印度]]第二大证券交易所 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ia.rediff.com/money/2006/jul/25quiz.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2007-03-16 |archive-date=2010-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211184247/http://ia.rediff.com/money/2006/jul/25quiz.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。NSE由一系列的印度主要金融机构、银行、保险公司和其他金融中介实际拥有，但作为单独实体经营运作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.geocities.com/kstability/student/illiquid/illiquid2.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2007-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919155322/http://www.geocities.com/kstability/student/illiquid/illiquid2.html |archive-date=2008-09-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2005年，NSE VSAT终端总数2799，覆盖印度超过超过320个城市<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nse-india.com/content/us/us_factsfigures.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2007-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061113122057/http://www.nse-india.com/content/us/us_factsfigures.htm |archive-date=2006-11-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2006年3月，NSE[[市场股本|市场股本]]总额438077亿[[印度卢比|印度卢比]]，成为[[南亚|南亚]]第二大股票市场<ref>http://www.nseindia.com/content/us/fact2006_sec1.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://www.nseindia.com/content/us/fact2006_sec1.pdf |date=20060824214906 }} NSE annual survey</ref>.

